description:
Here’s a recap of our second SciLearn Orientation Workshop from October 📸! We discussed the basics of learning, memory, and attention 🧠.

Make sure to check out our next SciLearn Workshop on December 3rd during the First Year Finals Fest 🎉! For more info, see the link in our bio.

Introducing the First Year Finals Fest! 🎉
Between December 2-4, SciLearn will be collaborating with the First Year Undergraduate Science Society (FUSS) on a series of events for all U0 and U1 students in Science courses! 📖💫

Each day, we will be hosting a new event to prepare you for a successfuly and healthy final assessment period.

Swipe for more info about each event, including Gingerbread House Building 🏠, Therapy Dogs 🐶, our third SciLearn Workshop about strategies for exam prep 📝, and a Final Exam Study Session 📚.

To register for the Gingerbread House Building and the SciLearn Workshop, visit the links in our bio!
